text: Aerenea impetiginosa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1868. It is known from Guatemala, Honduras, Colombia, Costa Rica, Mexico, Nicaragua, Panama, Peru, and Venezuela.BioLib.cz - Aerenea impetiginosa.
